The game starts with a screen that displays an image
 that invites the user to a button to start the game.
During the game the things we added extra are:
- Click indicator that indicates the same color even before clicking.
- Coloring of the signal pressed in a different color.
- A timer that flashes close to the end of time.
- Stop button if the user wants to go to the bathroom or eat.
 While pressing the button the letters are hidden.
Indicators for the various buttons on the board.
- End screen with a picture that warns of the end of the game.
- After a letter is clicked, the click indicator indicates only
 the words that can be clicked, ie only the neighboring letters.
- colorful board that invites the user to play.
